{"tid":946944,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"背部全裸出浴 阿Sa：效果幾震撼","createTime":"2018-12-19T01:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T14:32:51.000Z","uid":1886,"like":15,"dislike":167,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"cd6fd0603c852b60363f57003494cb1687ab53d9","tid":946944,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:49:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1391280/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1391280%2F&d=MgGw1fxvt6eEJPHkMJ7ZSp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=6ef729fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1391280%2F&h=4729909c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1391280/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181218/_2018121822394815522.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181218%2F_2018121822394815522.jpg&h=4369e510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蔡卓妍（阿Sa）繼《雛妓》後，於英皇電影《非分熟女》又一挑戰自我的突破之作。在首個預告片中， 阿Sa全裸坐在浴缸內背向鏡頭，但字幕對白說：「結婚4年了，依然是處女！」 隨即引起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n阿Sa直言接拍這片前已清楚了解角色及故事，只要符合劇情需要，又能表達其角色「小敏」的內心掙扎，她欣然接受這場大膽出浴戲。她說：「我接得這部戲，自然知道角色是怎樣，小敏在這一方面有點問題，她未至於性冷感，只是有些障礙而已。」<br />\n<br />\n對於背部全裸，阿Sa笑道：「前面黐晒嘢，好安全！不過，當日拍咗好幾個角度，效果都幾震撼！」"},{"pid":"0ac23acd633db2e63b17aa128b03e99392ecd341","tid":946944,"uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":80,"score":-75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:49:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181218/_2018121822395049569.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181218%2F_2018121822395049569.jpg&h=165a7f86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181218/_2018121822395098167.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=